xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">✨</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-rose transition-colors\">Prompt Engineer</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4\">Master the art of crafting effective prompts for AI models</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs mb-3\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dusty-pink/20 text-rose font-medium\">intermediate</span><span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">8-12 weeks</span></div></div></div><div class=\"card-base p-6 text-left hover:shadow-soft-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📈</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-rose transition-colors\">Business Intelligence Analyst</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4\">Analisis data bisnis, dashboarding, dan storytelling untuk pengambilan keputusan</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs mb-3\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dusty-pink/20 text-rose font-medium\">intermediate</span><span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">12-16 weeks</span></div></div></div><div class=\"card-base p-6 text-left hover:shadow-soft-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">💹</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-rose transition-colors\">Financial Data Analyst</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4\">Analisis data keuangan, forecasting, dan reporting untuk fungsi finance</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs mb-3\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dusty-pink/20 text-rose font-medium\">intermediate</span><span clas